&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Uputronics 1090MHz ADS-B Filtered Preamp &lt;a href="https://store.uputronics.com/index.php?route=product/product&amp;amp;product_id=50" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Store&lt;/a>
